script.name: plugin.guilds.docontested
script.sourceplaintext:
$Guilds.Data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' skip if $Guilds.Data return null
$table.sectors = $Guilds.Data['contested.sectors'] skip if $table.sectors return null
$current.time = playing time $sector = get next key: table=$table.sectors key=null while $sector $sector.data = $table.sectors[$sector]
$last.update = $sector.data[5] if ( $last.update + 120 ) < $current.time gosub sub.DoSector end
$sector = get next key: table=$table.sectors key=$sector end
return null
sub.DoSector: $size = size of array $sector.data if $size < 11 append 0 to array $sector.data end
$sector.data[5] = $current.time $table.dropped = $sector.data[8] $table.factions = $sector.data[2] *write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='Contested sector: %s, factions=%s', $sector, $table.factions, null, null, null $previous.owner = $sector.data[1] $start.time = $sector.data[3] $running.for = $current.time - $start.time $is.plot = $sector.data[4] $original.faction = $sector -> get local variable: name='original.owner'
* always add the previous owner to claim back if not $table.factions[$previous.owner] if not is fixed race: race=$previous.owner if $previous.owner != Player AND $previous.owner != Other if $running.for > 1800 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.claimsector : Sector=$sector Faction=$previous.owner else $rnd = random value from 0 to 1800 - 1 if $running.for > $rnd @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.claimsector : Sector=$sector Faction=$previous.owner end end end end end
* check for original faction timer $last.owner = $sector.data[10] if ( $last.owner + 240 ) < $current.time $faction.data = $table.factions[$previous.owner] *write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='Checking prevous faction, %s = %s', $previous.owner, $faction.data, null, null, null if $faction.data $value = $faction.data[2] inc $value = $faction.data[2] = $value $sector.data[10] = $current.time end end
if $sector.data[9] $sector.data[9] = [FALSE] $claimants = table alloc if $is.plot == 'assassin' $claimants[Pirates] = 110 $claimants[Split] = 110 $claimants[Paranid] = 110 else * should the original owner try? good chance too if not is fixed race: race=$original.faction if $original.faction != Player AND $original.faction != Other $claimants[$original.faction] = 70 end end
* find neighbours $aSectors = $sector -> find all sectors within 1 jumps: Only known sectors=[FALSE] if $aSectors $i = size of array $aSectors while $i dec $i = $sec = $aSectors[$i] if $sec != $sector $sec.owner = $sec -> get owner race if not $claimants[$sec.owner] if not is fixed race: race=$sec.owner if $sec.owner != Player AND $sec.owner != Other $claimants[$sec.owner] = 50 end end end end end end
* find other potention claimants end
$faction = get next key: table=$claimants key=null while $faction if not $table.dropped[$faction] if not $table.factions[$faction] $chance = $claimants[$faction] $rnd = random value from 0 to 100 - 1 if $rnd <= $chance if $is.plot == 'assassin' $table.factions[$faction] = 200 else $table.factions[$faction] = 2700 end end end end $faction = get next key: table=$claimants key=$faction end end
$starting.values = table alloc if $is.plot == 'assassin' $starting.values[Paranid] = 6500 $starting.values[Split] = 4750 $starting.values[Pirates] = 3000 end
* find all factions set to [TRUE] and add them over time $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=null while $faction $faction.data = $table.factions[$faction] if not is datatype[ $faction.data ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $rnd = random value from 0 to $faction.data - 1 if $running.for > $rnd remove key $faction from table $table.factions $value = $starting.values[$faction] skip if $value $value = 0 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.claimsector : Sector=$sector Faction=$faction Starting Value=$value break end end $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=$faction end
$original.faction = $sector -> get local variable: name='original.owner' gosub sub.DoActions gosub sub.CheckDocks gosub sub.CheckWin endsub
sub.CheckDocks: $tDocks = $sector ->get dock table from sector if $tDocks $dock = get next key: table=$tDocks key=null while $dock $started = $dock -> get local variable: name='claim.start' if not $started $dock ->set local variable: name='claim.start' value=$current.time else if ( $started + 300 ) < $current.time $dock.owner = $dock -> get owner race $faction.data = $table.factions[$dock.owner] if $faction.data $value = $faction.data[2] $rnd = random value from 90 to 110 - 1 $value = $value + $rnd $faction.data[2] = $value end end $dock = get next key: table=$tDocks key=$dock end end endsub
sub.CheckWin: $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=null while $faction $faction.data = $table.factions[$faction] if is datatype[ $faction.data ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY $value = $faction.data[2] if $value >= 10000 @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.sectorclaim : Sector=$sector Faction=$faction break end *write to player logbook: printf: type=[Log.Debug], fmt='Contested sector, faction=%s, value=%s', $faction, $value, $faction.data, null, null end $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=$faction end endsub
sub.DoActions: $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=null while $faction $faction.data = $table.factions[$faction] if is datatype[ $faction.data ] == DATATYPE_ARRAY gosub sub.DoAction end $faction = get next key: table=$table.factions key=$faction end endsub
sub.DoAction: $current.time = playing time $next.time = $faction.data[1] if $current.time > $next.time $action = 1
if $action == 1 end end endsub
return null
